= 8.0 + 46.0 - 0.3
= 54.0 - 0.3
= 53.7

@pwharris #mathstratchat  We used an "Over, Over" strategy.
as 7.8 = 8 - 0.2 and 45.9 = 46-0.1
so 7.8 + 45.9
= 8.0 - 0.2 + 46.0 - 0.1
= 8.0 + 46.0 - 0.3
= 54.0 - 0.3
= 53.7
Play with it hereüß°: https://t.co/TVJvrS7h7A
